msgctxt "mn1:27.1"
msgid "Yopi so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sekkho appattamānaso anuttaraṃ yogakkhemaṃ patthayamāno viharati, sopi pathaviṃ pathavito abhijānāti; "
msgstr "A mendicant who is a trainee, who hasn’t achieved their heart’s desire, but lives aspiring to the supreme sanctuary, directly knows earth as earth. "

#. VAR: maññi → vā maññati (si) | māmaññī (s1)
#. VAR: abhiññāya → abhiññatvā (si, mr)
#. VAR: mābhinandi → vā abhinandati (si) | mābhinandī (s1)
msgctxt "mn1:27.2"
msgid "pathaviṃ pathavito abhiññāya pathaviṃ mā maññi, pathaviyā mā maññi, pathavito mā maññi, pathaviṃ meti mā maññi, pathaviṃ mābhinandi. "
msgstr "But they shouldn’t identify with earth, they shouldn’t identify regarding earth, they shouldn’t identify as earth, they shouldn’t identify that ‘earth is mine’, they shouldn’t take pleasure in earth. "

msgctxt "mn1:27.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "mn1:27.4"
